ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 9 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Stage 9, Arc-et-Senans to Besancon. This year's Tour includes two long individual time trials which will reshape the overall standings. Today's is the first of them - 41.5 km of twisting and turning roads but largely flat. Expect Britain's Bradley Wiggins to show his class today.
